# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-operational-maturity
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Define the operational maturity model for the cluster. This helps guide
#   long-term improvements and ensures the system evolves predictably.
#
# Maturity Levels:
#
#   Level 1 — Basic
#     - Manual builds
#     - Minimal diagnostics
#
#   Level 2 — Structured
#     - Distributed builds
#     - Preflight checks
#     - Basic rollback
#
#   Level 3 — Observability
#     - Full diagnostics suite
#     - Drift detection
#     - Kernel introspection
#
#   Level 4 — Automation
#     - Automated deploy/rollback
#     - Automated verification
#
#   Level 5 — Resilience
#     - Incident response workflows
#     - Capacity planning
#     - Integrity verification
#
# Notes:
#   - This file defines the long-term operational roadmap.
# =============================================================================
